Konseco Inc. De say e dey call for di redemption on top of di 800,000 remaining shares of di $1.875 series A convertible preferred stock at $26,805 a share.

Insurance mean sey all conversion right on top di stock go terminate on Nov. 30.

Before den, Conseco talk sey di stock still dey convertible to common stock at di rate of 1.439 share of di common stock, wey dey equivalent to di conversion of $17.50 to di common stock.

For New York Stock Exchange trading Friday, Conseco close at $19.50, down 25 cents.

